<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT96">
<l>iṉiyaṟintē ṉīcaṟkum nāṉmukaṟkun teyva</l>
<l>miṉiyaṟintē ṉemperumā ṉuṉṉai yiṉiyaṟintēṉ</l>
<l>kāraṇaṉnī kaṟṟavainī kaṟpavainī naṟkiricai</l>
<l>nāraṇaṉnī naṉkaṟintēṉ nāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have now understood [You as being] Śiva’s and the four-faced [Brahmā]’s God!</l>
<l>I have now understood You, O our Lord! I have now understood</l>
<l>that You are the Cause, You are what was learnt, You are what is learnt,</l>
<l>You are Nārāyaṇa of good actions. I have well understood [all this].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
